        "author": "Scott Grocott x- @scott_grocott",
        "description": "Mountain City is on the island of Autopia. Autopia is a socially stratified island nation where car culture dominates daily life. The city is known for its towering skyscrapers, sprawling highways, and dense urban environment filled with neon lights and bustling streets. The story follows a lone protagonist navigating the dangerous underbelly of Mountain City, uncovering conspiracies tied to the powerful automotive families that control the city's economy and politics.",
